      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 588550.0,
      "end_time": 590780.0,
      "text": "Even educated, cosmopolitan folks like"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 590780.0,
      "end_time": 592180.0,
      "text": "Sefa believe in this."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 611610.0,
      "end_time": 613410.0,
      "text": "THOMAS MORTON: Besides, is of any of this really that much"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 613410.0,
      "end_time": 616750.0,
      "text": "weirder than shit like communion or circumcisions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 616750.0,
      "end_time": 625370.0,
      "text": "[CRYING]"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 632320.0,
      "end_time": 634320.0,
      "text": "THOMAS MORTON: That part was a little rough."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 640526.0,
      "end_time": 644860.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 644860.0,
      "end_time": 646410.0,
      "text": "THOMAS MORTON: While Sakawa originally referred to a very"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 646410.0,
      "end_time": 649730.0,
      "text": "specific type of internet fraud mixed with juju, then it"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 649730.0,
      "end_time": 652330.0,
      "text": "went on to mean any internet crime involving witchcraft,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 652330.0,
      "end_time": 654650.0,
      "text": "and now it&#39;s kind of evolved into its own full-blown"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 654650.0,
      "end_time": 656550.0,
      "text": "subculture."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 656550.0,
      "end_time": 659960.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s Sakawa music, Sakawa movies, Sakawa cars, a"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 659960.0,
      "end_time": 661280.0,
      "text": "Sakawa style of dressing."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 685440.0,
      "end_time": 686700.0,
      "text": "THOMAS MORTON: Right now Ghana&#39;s in the throes of"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 686700.0,
      "end_time": 687370.0,
      "text": "Sakawa mania."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 687370.0,
      "end_time": 689340.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s in all the papers and movie theaters."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 689340.0,
      "end_time": 690590.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s bigger than rap."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 693510.0,
      "end_time": 697700.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m looking for Sakawa movies."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 697700.0,
      "end_time": 699270.0,
      "text": "Oh, cool, here&#39;s number three."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 699270.0,
      "end_time": 701810.0,
      "text": "If you want a glimpse at just how deeply Sakawa&#39;s penetrated"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 701810.0,
      "end_time": 703660.0,
      "text": "the public consciousness, check this out."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 703660.0,
      "end_time": 706670.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re already up to &quot;Sakawa Boys 8,&quot; and the series just"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 706670.0,
      "end_time": 707920.0,
      "text": "started last year."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 712750.0,
      "end_time": 716190.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re on our way to meet a guy who makes films about Sakawa."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 716190.0,
      "end_time": 717670.0,
      "text": "His name is Socrate Safo."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 717670.0,
      "end_time": 722180.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s actually like the Martin Scorsese of Ghanaian internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 722180.0,
      "end_time": 725750.0,
      "text": "fraud-based, gangster films."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 725750.0,
      "end_time": 728900.0,
      "text": "The Ghanaian film industry, or Ghallywood, operates on kind"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 728900.0,
      "end_time": 731700.0,
      "text": "of a &quot;more is more&quot; principle of movie making."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 731700.0,
      "end_time": 733840.0,
      "text": "They crank out hundreds of titles a year, most of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 733840.0,
      "end_time": 736410.0,
      "text": "shot on zero budget in as quickly as a couple weeks from"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 736410.0,
      "end_time": 738490.0,
      "text": "start to finish."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 738490.0,
      "end_time": 740550.0,
      "text": "This speed doesn&#39;t do much for production values, but it does"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 740550.0,
      "end_time": 742680.0,
      "text": "allow them to respond to current events and to cater"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 742680.0,
      "end_time": 746694.0,
      "text": "their subject matter to their countrymen&#39;s exact interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 781110.0,
      "end_time": 782180.0,
      "text": "THOMAS MORTON: Realistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 782180.0,
      "end_time": 784430.0,
      "text": "Things drawn from real life."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 883722.0,
      "end_time": 886590.0,
      "text": "-Ain&#39;t you got nothing better to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 886590.0,
      "end_time": 887840.0,
      "text": "You asked for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 890615.0,
      "end_time": 894460.0,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 894460.0,
      "end_time": 896610.0,
      "text": "THOMAS MORTON: Socrate&#39;s movie touched a nerve in national"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 896610.0,
      "end_time": 899710.0,
      "text": "psyche and brought the issue of Sakawa to life for a lot of"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 899710.0,
      "end_time": 901410.0,
      "text": "Ghanaians who otherwise wouldn&#39;t have heard of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 935592.0,
      "end_time": 941520.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 941520.0,
      "end_time": 943230.0,
      "text": "THOMAS MORTON: Since being thrust into the mainstream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 943230.0,
      "end_time": 945760.0,
      "text": "though, Sakawa has drawn a huge outcry from government"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 945760.0,
      "end_time": 949290.0,
      "text": "officials, tabloids, and Christian preachers, whose"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 949290.0,
      "end_time": 951160.0,
      "text": "billboards in Accra are almost as ubiquitous as ads for"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 951160.0,
      "end_time": 953165.0,
      "text": "computer classes and juju priests."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 989030.0,
      "end_time": 991130.0,
      "text": "THOMAS MORTON: While the furor over Sakawa dominates the"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 991130.0,
      "end_time": 994130.0,
      "text": "tabloids and pulpits, the focus is all on black magic"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 994130.0,
      "end_time": 996330.0,
      "text": "and blood debts and Sakawa boys turning each other into"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 996330.0,
      "end_time": 998270.0,
      "text": "goats and snakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 998270.0,
      "end_time": 1000440.0,
      "text": "None of it tackles the root of the problem, the fact that"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 1000440.0,
      "end_time": 1002480.0,
      "text": "over a third of young Ghanaians are unemployed, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 1002480.0,
      "end_time": 1004300.0,
      "text": "what jobs there are are filled by corrupt government"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 1004300.0,
      "end_time": 1005850.0,
      "text": "officials and their cousins."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 1035589.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1037130.9999999999,
      "text": "THOMAS MORTON: Up until now the government&#39;s been more"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 1037130.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1040200.0000000001,
      "text": "than happy to turn a blind eye to Sakawa since it&#39;s basically"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 1040200.0,
      "end_time": 1043440.0,
      "text": "providing regular work for people that they can&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 1043440.0,
      "end_time": 1045359.0,
      "text": "There are also persistent rumors that Sakawa isn&#39;t just"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 1045359.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1048030.9999999999,
      "text": "limited to gangs of teenage delinquents, but is actually a"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 1048030.0,
      "end_time": 1050570.0,
      "text": "popular sideline among policemen, soldiers and"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 1050570.0,
      "end_time": 1052430.0,
      "text": "politicians."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 1070180.0,
      "end_time": 1071810.0,
      "text": "THOMAS MORTON: Now that&#39;s Sakawa&#39;s threatening Ghana&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 1071810.0,
      "end_time": 1074350.0,
      "text": "business reputation, the government&#39;s cracking down."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 1074350.0,
      "end_time": 1077320.0,
      "text": "And them and the press have started a moral panic over it."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 1077320.0,
      "end_time": 1079820.0,
      "text": "Just like gangsta rappers in the early &#39;90s, Sakawa boys"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 1079820.0,
      "end_time": 1083080.0,
      "text": "have gone from objects of sort of cultural fascination to"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 1083080.0,
      "end_time": 1085410.0,
      "text": "scapegoats for all their country&#39;s ills."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 1132170.0,
      "end_time": 1134419.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 1182630.0,
      "end_time": 1184030.0,
      "text": "THOMAS MORTON: The end of Sakawa may not necessarily"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 1184030.0,
      "end_time": 1186680.0,
      "text": "bring juju Armageddon to Ghana, but it will leave a"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 1186680.0,
      "end_time": 1188980.0,
      "text": "bunch of angry young men without any source of steady"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 1188980.0,
      "end_time": 1194130.0,
      "text": "income, which is arguably even scarier."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 1194130.0,
      "end_time": 1197070.0,
      "text": "On a lighter note, Ghana just discovered oil off its shore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 1197070.0,
      "end_time": 1199870.0,
      "text": "so maybe that&#39;ll solve all their problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 1199870.0,
      "end_time": 1209870.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    }
  ]
}